   Second Black Mamba call of the day! This was the fourth (second catch of the day) in Newlands West (Durban), bordering a beautiful valley. It slithered into this storeroom and gave all the residents a fright- imagine how the snake felt! A nice long specimen, but worryingly underweight. It's going to need some TLC before release. #blackmamba #mambas #dendroaspispolylepis #venomous #venomoussnakes #durban #southafrica #africa #onlyinafrica #kzn #reptiles #reptilesofinstagram #conservation #wildlife #monday #mondaymotivation #animalsofinstagram #nature #summer #heat #hotsummer

